l><mxCell id="e13" value="give merely-possible future people no weight" style="edgeStyle=none;curved=1;html=1;endArrow=block;endFill=1;strokeColor=#9aa6b3;fontSize=9;fontColor=#5b6675;strokeColor=#8a5fb0;" edge="1" parent="1" source="w1_2_5_6_8_15_16" target="w1_2_5_6_8_15_16_17"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"><Array as="points"><mxPoint x="897" y="1803"/><mxPoint x="895" y="1849"/></Array></mxGeometry></mxCell><object label="Suffering-focused&lt;br&gt;ethics&lt;br&gt;[1+2+5+6+8]&lt;br&gt;→ AI safety (Redwood Research)&lt;br&gt;   86k lives-eq/$1k · 47% best&lt;br&gt;   runner-up ALLFED · 34%&lt;br&gt;(Brian Tomasik, David Pearce)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + no_discounting_future_humans + suffering_focused&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Asymmetry: averting intense suffering takes priority over creating happiness. Factory farming, malaria and the worst wild-animal conditions weigh up; speculative future-flourishing bets weigh down. Arises most naturally from taking animal suffering seriously, so it requires animals_somewhat. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 8 suffering_focused" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWG1z2zYS%2Fis7nmtPSmWKpN7l880osdxm6qQZ27lOJ8ooEAlJqCmCBUDTutT97bcASImy5DNTfdFQJPDss6%2FYxdeTkM5JGqk3PKQnw5NmE87Pz%2BFWEBaD4hAI8t81PmQxTFLf9dqQcRGF94xmkHlTf9qZdqd9qEnFE%2BjX9eZJjCAjKdNVohiPIVgi1hBcSIjgwZKRSEN5Ax88mBMxJRlZT5fpisSy%2BOADidmKRHIq%2BYpmS6KKLx2YpyoVNN8wXRGlqJhmTC2nIZMBT2PF4kWxvAsxL7%2Bf7uwuVvVBpvM5FWYBD1JJQ6PEmARLIFtNmAQCH9Zqic9zFlFAG20%2FyyYozZSEoWyAoGhYFlMJXBgwQU%2FRAGRFkS%2BT%2BF4tqbXNPyUqFQcG4wwCvkq41DpsFuDeOKSIiK%2BYNGhSkTgkEY8prNBzkQNfNo4Z33%2FRVPV2%2BpDQQOHGexKlFPjcIGx96Biw11QqmKVrSLUYvVHSsmJDGL0FSeZUraF2TcOM8xCucRERwbJuMX4cvx9fj27HFzBbw4LGVBBFnWRdhA0Nmdox1iv82ED3KEtJ2xORDNbHOKBCacVXXGC4bOwm7VprFJIkEaPSgZv1yon4IuYCQ6b2Nek0IBl0H