t astronomical stakes now attenuates them: future-facing value is multiplied by the probability the simulation keeps running, and the ranking slides back toward the present. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 8 suffering_focused → 15 space_expansion_backfires → 16 living_in_simulation" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJzFWWtz27gV%2FSt3PN1WSm2ZlKyXXXfGieXdTJ1sxnaa2YkzCkRCImqSYAHSijab%2Fe09AEiJsuSJtpppv3hoAjj33Cfupb4ehHzKijh%2FJUN%2BcHpwfEzn5%2Bd0p5hIKZcUKPbrAg%2FzlO6Ltuef0FyqOHwUfE5zf9wed8e98WDsd8d%2Bjxo6lxn5vabBuE%2BBdaF1kWS5kCkFESBPyaOMKRlEgsUG0R%2B2yacpU2M2Z4txVCQs1dVCm1gqEhbrsZYJn0csr1a6NC3yQvHywDhhec7VeC7yaBwKHcgizUU6q7b3KJX19%2BO109WuAeliOuXKbpBBoXm4pNglnbGAj%2FmXDCegz3jCgoepUHx5HAaIxaM5LNKxFkkRM6O4tcOIBRGxlTGEJkbvFnmE56mIOcHaq2V9TLlRloWhPiTF4SKRQpBUFkzxI9iQJRwqC433ecSdef%2BiYZc0sBhnFMgkk9qYYbkBZ9OQAxGvhLZoOmdpyGKZckoQA3GLPi9dPHr8bKia41CcBzkOPrK44CSnFmEVDS0L9pLrnCbFggojxhzUvK7YKV28Js2mPF9Q44aHcylDusEmpoKo6TB%2BHL0d3VzcjS5psqAZT7liOW9liyoAeSjyNWO9wOIhPJw7SsaeQLJY79OAq9wonkiFiFvaTbu9zigsy2LBdYtuF0krlrNUKkRd42vWPaRs2P3WtFjWZ0PvB3r1%2BszunPCcubeZkhM2EbHIQWQijfKhyZ6P3iH5n1p0xYJcQiZT3EFhQ2Y8keaHpCVxEx5SzeC%2F0cf55cX1L8d%2F%2BkQTHss5csOctX7mX%2FAcL3Ac2LCtxYLssAhy5xH4kCM%2Bof40lgVORXD%2FZRn4dL6pIBKy5Q2smuZx8K1JZEMMmNBhzsUsAjbSV3FmUyqCtUw0amrcyYRp8XBG%2F4RCZq3ttT0Ya5lG75QAdfh6q2S%2F5ZeCe61uKZh%2FyRWriWWP8J%2BBhs48RTAtsZ8X75K7prVvoTO8PMpFwumvFLCc6VzJDBYzpSMtbK4aiahFRw6hDPXGDUs0XxzfImxS%2Bt374Xih6FHTW6nCiBWafvdbXfPyDILOEYdUVRpjClM1Xpal4g3qrDChpp51RXvpil5pkVyJxPBaS8KS4DwytQPJg6BYViZTH5hKXNpG7FemQmpc8iJM%2BQIBFhYsPipsWkIhKcJjqSYiR3KIdKqMVRBNAD%2BjDxx%2BVjpBUdWGQWSjUSHSppCBA5rH0yPjEBEIngYITG1UXpa%2BV9JU2wKRe75MmAZ8PnSavWustpIqUIhRhWbEU1nMIppKWz%2BsRKdus6oAL6XxXQJ%2Fe50y0S9hXiQBR3AENnBqKZXBgkwtkE8pN1TxfEgvR1c%2F34xcWbAILuYQRoewDHI6wZWT5ke4WYIIFl%2B6im7fv3lzcfOLSzhUaScEhfCBhxZpInMeUMNkIl28vUQYKcFQiFz%2BNlt0Z9Qq4rjM7aPJ4sg9EYqmeHQGcbo6avCAU8htszrJR55a