al stakes now attenuates them: future-facing value is multiplied by the probability the simulation keeps running, and the ranking slides back toward the present. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 8 suffering_focused → 16 living_in_simulation" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJy1WG1z27gR%2Fis7nl4rpTJNUu923RnHlu8ydXIe2%2BnNTZxRIBIScSYJFgAtqznfb%2B8CICXKoidMNfdFQ5HAs8%2B%2BYhdfD0I6J3msznlID44Pjo7g9PQU7gRhKSgOgSD%2FXeHDMoX73He9Hiy5iMNHRpew9Kb%2BtD8dTEdTbwAtqXgG3qCtAe5TBDqTMk8yxXgKQYR4x%2BBCRgQPIkZiDeeNffBgTsSULMlqGuUJSWX5wQeSsoTEcip5QpcRUeWXPsxzlQtabJgmRCkqpkumomnIZMDzVLF0US4fQMqr76dbu8tVI5D5fE6FWcCDXNJwTXEAMXvUH1g6lSzJY6KVMjpOSBAB2SjKJBC4XqkIn%2BcspoBm3HyWR6C0IiQMZQcERduzlErgwoAJeoj2IQlFdZjE9yqi1nR%2Fk6hzGhiMEwh4knGpVVwvwL1pSBERXzFp0KQiaUhinlJI0LmxA1%2FWvps8ftFU9Xb6lNFA4cZHEucU%2BNwgbNzsGLC3VCqY5SvItRi9UdKqYsdw9g4kmVO1gtYNDZech3CDi4gIorbF%2BHHyYXJzdje5gNkKFjSlgijqZKsysmjI1Jax3uDHDnpPWUranohksD6mARVKK55wgdG0tpu0a61RSJbFjEoHbleJE%2FNFygVGVOtr1u9ANu4%2Ftw2W8dnY%2FQHO352YlTOqiH2bCT4jMxYzhURmXCsf6rT45HbA%2B%2BzAJQkUR5lEUAuFCzLtiVR1QHKgOjy4WKD%2FJp%2BWF2dXvx795TPMaMyXGPd6r%2FEzfcLneIXbERtta7BQdpgHynoEfUgxWlH9ecxz3BWh%2By%2BKoIbTXQUx2Rx3ZNTUj6PnNoAJMcREHZaULSLExtQUlJh0idBaOholtO54QiR7OIF%2Fo0L6m%2B%2F6LhprnSLXgiF19HWtZM%2FxCsEDp18Ipk9KkIpY8oj%2B09CoM00xmNbYr4u3iVvR2jPQGb48VCyh8HcIiCJSCZ6hxXRZSHOTq1oi1plDi1CEeuuGJJKujm4xbFL4w%2F3haCXgUcIHLsKI5BL%2B8Jy%2BfnmCgk4xDqGsItoU6zpwznVZydGNp%2BvoaaEBxlbx69ZmKYgcKw6m5AJoyvNFBHNukkmTK6pau0yHt1wrkqDybreI%2BgsmMFeBoqUCY8VKfGUCq6VYYXClWFUChs8deDu5%2FPlmYnPEIFgHoE07mGkY4AnW1lQdYgkNIgyLtSPh9uP792c3v9row5JlhWBVeKChQZpxRQNo6bCEsw8XaFPBCGalDea2A3darTyOi0A%2FnK0O7RNgBWGP1iBWV0sN67dVyC4zOvFHmhpUrGWYULnAx8I%2BWJPR5vqYQkExS0ti8j85WyxiemQYyqN%2FsPCfTvnSlkKTm1hsMMd10UHFEebnDxPIYmJlFfWYhLpWUYzV1aYiYuUmKFM7DnVnKco2CJi7dqUttxgjPM%2F%2BxbRl0wsSr66p%2BCjD%2BpQZOAN%2FPO6O%2BuOR53eHrkcP3f46e13XG45Hw27Pc4fDvucPvV6RVi%2F8h7XTBEFRMzS