t;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Person-affecting population ethics: making happy people is neutral, so the astronomical case for x-risk reduction — which rests on the sheer number of extra future lives saved from extinction — loses almost all its force. Only the harm to people who exist regardless still counts. This is the standard premise longtermism&#x27;s critics deny (discussed as the key objection in Greaves &amp; MacAskill&#x27;s &#x27;The Case for Strong Longtermism&#x27;). It requires no_discounting_future_humans, the astronomical-stakes move it pushes back on. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 8 suffering_focused → 16 living_in_simulation → 17 person_affecting_view" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJy9WWtz2kgW%2FSu3XDu74AEsgXnZ661ybDyTGifjsp2dmgop0kgN9Fqotd2SMZNxfvuebkkgjFwhS9V8SRGp%2B9xz3%2FfKXw58PmFJEF9Inx%2BcHBwd0dnZGd0rJkKKJXmK%2FbHEj0VIw6TpuMe0kCrwHwVf0MIdNUftUWfUG7mdkdulio5lRG63ajCGIbDOtU7mUSxkSN4MkCfkUMSU9GaCBQbR7TfJpQlTI7Zgy9EsmbNQ5y%2BaxEIxZ4EeaTnnixmL8zdtmiRxonh2YTRncczVaCHi2cgX2pNJGItwmh%2FvUCiLz0cbt%2FNTPdLJZMKVPSC9RHN%2FRbFDgXg0L0Q40mKeBMwqlb%2FuUsSVluGIAcCzIoyJrA0GzJsRWxtCaGJ0s4xn%2BD0RASdYev1aH1FsFGW%2Br2ukONwjQq5JKgumeB32Y3MOdYXG83jGU9P%2BQ8MmoWcxTsmT80hqY4LVAdwNfQ5EPBLaoumYhT4LZMhpDv8HDfq8cu%2Fg8bOhaq7zpwhK4eIjCxJOcmIR1pHQsGBvuI5pnCwpMWLMRc2Lip3QPbB%2BNibndM3ZNOHpxZ8G7we35%2FeDSxovacpDrljMG9Eyjzjui3jDQod4WYNL45SHMSKQLNaH0OMqNtrOpUKIrYyl07OpJVgUBYLrBt0t541ATkOpEGaVL1G7RlG%2F%2FVy1WNZRfecHunh7ak%2BOeczSp5GSYzYWgYhBZCyNxr5Jl49OjdxPDbpiXiwhkymeQuFAZMwfxjXSkriJCammcNrg4%2BLy%2FPr3o799ojEP5ALJYO5a5%2FIn%2FA6WuA5sGNRiQbafeHHqBjiOI4Sh%2FiSQCW7N4PPLLNLpbFtBZGDD6Vk1zc%2Fec5XIxhUwocOCi%2BkM2MhXxZnNoRmsZUJQU%2BVezpkWD6f0byhk3jWdpgNjrfLmRglQj5flkt2GmwnuNNqZYP4UK1YQyx7hPwMNnXmICFphvy4%2BzeaC1q6FjvCwHos5px%2FJYzHTsZIRLGZqRZikCWxykKl6ipDFd%2BWWzTVfHt0hbEL66vxwtFT0qOm9VP6MJZq%2Buo22eXgKQWeIQ8pLizHFqjhcSFNrErjxbBU9FRignyp%2BUynUEZWgDCEPp8RDmUxn